starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Pillar pages provide a comprehensive overview of a topic in the most effective way possible. With no more than 2,000 words, pillar pages help create content suitable for a brand\u2019s target audience.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-c2ab255 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"c2ab255\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-34cba3c\" data-id=\"34cba3c\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f1636b8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"f1636b8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Content pillars and pillar pages are handy tools in marketing. Nevertheless, understanding how they work is essential before using them effectively. Let\u2019s get started.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-42be486 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"42be486\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Why are Content Pillars and Pillar Pages Useful for Social Media Marketers?<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-720082a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"720082a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">One of the most important objectives for social media marketers is gaining followers. Having more followers is a sign that the brand is on the right path. This shows that the brand is growing, and growth is what keeps them alive. But how can brands attract more people?<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When it comes to digital marketing, you must provide valuable content. Your content attracts more followers, exposes your business to more people, and engages them. All of this benefits you and your brand.\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To make this possible, you must organize and prepare your content. Content pillars will help social media marketers remain focused on their brand\u2019s purpose and values. <\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2c6c981 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"2c6c981\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">How to Create Content Pillars in Social Media\n<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-eedee96 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"eedee96\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Get ready to create content pillars and start using them, as we have created a list of tips to help you achieve it!<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2f51ca1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"2f51ca1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">1. Get to Know Your Audience<\/h3>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-07846b6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"07846b6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To properly start planning your content pillars, you need to know your audience. If this is unclear, you won\u2019t know where to start or if you are on the right track.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">How can you identify your followers? Start doing interviews or surveys. This way, you can collect valuable data: what they like, what they don\u2019t like, what they would want to learn, and so on. It gives you an understanding of what you must focus on to bring value.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You can use some questions to get started:<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ae4be40 elementor-icon-list--layout-traditional elementor-list-item-link-full_width elementor-widget elementor-widget-icon-list\" data-id=\"ae4be40\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"icon-list.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"elementor-icon-list-items\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"elementor-icon-list-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-icon\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-dot-circle\"><\/i>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-text\">What does my target audience expect from my brand?<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"elementor-icon-list-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-icon\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-dot-circle\"><\/i>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-text\">In which ways can my brand\u2019s social media content help my target audience?<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"elementor-icon-list-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-icon\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-dot-circle\"><\/i>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-text\">Which topics do my target audience want my brand to work on?<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"elementor-icon-list-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-icon\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-dot-circle\"><\/i>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-text\">Which platforms are my target audience using?<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/ul>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c42be67 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"c42be67\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Knowing your audience is the first step to reach them!<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2d7fe6e elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"2d7fe6e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">2. Identify 5 Pillars of Content<\/h3>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6dfc77c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"6dfc77c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Now that you know your audience, you need to start creating your content. Take a look at this: <\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f966b60 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"f966b60\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"512\" height=\"202\" src=\"https:\/\/creasquare.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/5-pillars-of-content.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-17676\" alt=\"5 pillars of content\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https:\/\/creasquare.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/5-pillars-of-content.png 512w, https:\/\/creasquare.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/5-pillars-of-content-300x118.png 300w, https:\/\/creasquare.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/5-pillars-of-content-440x174.png 440w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-70e7a99 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"70e7a99\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">These five pillars are used to categorize social media content. How do they work? Let\u2019s imagine your brand sells handbags and purses. You might want to divide your content pillars like this:<\/span><\/p><ol><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Promotional pillar: promote a new product.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Educational pillar: share facts about handbags.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Community pillar: share news about your products.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Entertainment pillar: make entertaining content or share entertaining things about your products.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Engagement pillar: interact with your followers.<\/span><\/li><\/ol><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This way, you have plenty of content ideas to work on, but it still needs to be organized!<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f2b3bb9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"f2b3bb9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">3. Planning with a Content Calendar<\/h3>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ad068ea elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ad068ea\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Once you\u2019ve got the ideas of the content you want to create, you need to organize them. Instead of thinking about what you should post each day at the last minute, try making a <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/later.com\/blog\/social-media-content-calendar\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">content calendar<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> for each month of the year and balance out the use of your pillars to generate engagement. This way, you can organize and have your upcoming works ready to post. <\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9049695 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"9049695\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"512\" height=\"405\" src=\"https:\/\/creasquare.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/Creasquare-content-calendar.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-17677\" alt=\"Creasquare content calendar\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https:\/\/creasquare.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/Creasquare-content-calendar.png 512w, https:\/\/creasquare.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/Creasquare-content-calendar-300x237.png 300w, https:\/\/creasquare.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/Creasquare-content-calendar-440x348.png 440w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-92482aa elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"92482aa\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Creasquare content calendar<\/strong><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9c7f110 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"9c7f110\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">There are different ways to create your content calendar. You can do it the traditional way, which is writing it down on a piece of paper and making a physical planner or printed calendar, or use <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.microsoft.com\/en-us\/microsoft-365\/excel\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Excel<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> spreadsheets or <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.google.com\/sheets\/about\/#:~:text=Google%20Sheets%3A%20Online%20Spreadsheet%20Editor&amp;text=Google%20Workspace&amp;text=An%20integrated%20suit%20of%20secure,apps%20powered%20by%20Google%20AI.\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Google Sheets<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> (shown in the example above), or you can even use a social media tool like <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/creasquare.io\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Creasquare<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> to create your content and draft your post directly in the app before you schedule it.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c9e4548 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"c9e4548\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>I encourage you to try out <a href=\"https:\/\/creasquare.io\/content-calendar\/\">Creasquare content calendar<\/a> to plan your posts and automate your process, it really makes a difference!<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-043f894 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"043f894\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">4. Check Out Your Competition\n<\/h3>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7c7d852 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"7c7d852\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you have your content created and organized, it is most likely that your competitors have it as well. For that reason, it is a must to check on your competition and see what works for them. <\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Seeing how they develop themselves and the marketing techniques they use can inspire you and also help you in the development of your content pillars.\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Take notes on what your competition is doing, what they are not doing, and what they are trying to improve.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7eaa5ad elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"7eaa5ad\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">5. Pay Attention to Trends and News<\/h3>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3d51880 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3d51880\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Besides paying attention to your followers\u2019 interests, you must be up to date with what\u2019s happening around the world.\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trends and news can help you stay relevant in social media. One way of knowing what is trending is by checking <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/trends.google.com\/trends\/?geo=AR\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Google Trends<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. See what the world is searching for on the internet and think if you can relate it to your work. <\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4c9b38e elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"4c9b38e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">6. Take Advantage of Social Media\n<\/h3>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6509452 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"6509452\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Social media has many tools that can help you interact with your followers. The more apps you use, the better.\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">For example, creating <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/about.instagram.com\/features\/reels\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Reels<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, photos, and carousels on <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/about.instagram.com\/about-us\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Instagram<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> can help with the growth of your brand. At the same time, using Instagram \u2018<\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/about.instagram.com\/features\/stories\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">polls\u2019, \u2018questions\u2019, or \u2018quizzes<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u2019 on stories will strengthen the bond with your audience due to the interaction between your brand and them. <\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9fbe17d elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"9fbe17d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"261\" height=\"512\" src=\"https:\/\/creasquare.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/social-media-story-options.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-17678\" alt=\"Social media story options\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https:\/\/creasquare.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/social-media-story-options.png 261w, https:\/\/creasquare.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/social-media-story-options-153x300.png 153w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 261px) 100vw, 261px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-efcf15a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"efcf15a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Another social media example that is quite trendy and can help your brand become more relevant is <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.tiktok.com\/about\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">TikTok<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. This social network has become an incredible marketing tool that offers new ways to reach customers. Creating videos of 15 seconds to 3 minutes can attract your target audience if you <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/creasquare.io\/blog\/10-strategies-to-get-more-views-on-tiktok\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">learn how to use the TikTok algorithm<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> to your advantage. If the content appeals to your audience, your growth will be assured.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d856ae6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"d856ae6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"259\" height=\"512\" src=\"https:\/\/creasquare.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/brand-using-tiktok-example.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-17679\" alt=\"Brand using tiktok example\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https:\/\/creasquare.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/brand-using-tiktok-example.jpeg 259w, https:\/\/creasquare.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/brand-using-tiktok-example-152x300.jpeg 152w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 259px) 100vw, 259px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1bffc53 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"1bffc53\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">What Results Do Brands That Use Content Pillars Get?\n<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bcc180c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"bcc180c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As we have seen before, there are many benefits of using content pillars on social media. Let\u2019s see how these two brands use content pillars and how they benefit from it:<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-57b973a elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"57b973a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"507\" height=\"512\" src=\"https:\/\/creasquare.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/starbucks-instagram-account.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-17680\" alt=\"Starbucks Instagram account\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https:\/\/creasquare.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/starbucks-instagram-account.png 507w, https:\/\/creasquare.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/starbucks-instagram-account-297x300.png 297w, https:\/\/creasquare.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/starbucks-instagram-account-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/creasquare.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/starbucks-instagram-account-440x444.png 440w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 507px) 100vw, 507px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8c80c6e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"8c80c6e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Above, we can see <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/starbucks\/?hl=es-la\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Starbuck\u2019s Instagram account<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. This brand is known for coffee and unique beverages. Even though they are a renowned brand, they still have to use as many marketing tools as possible to keep attracting more customers. <\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">On their Instagram account, they share many things. Starbucks is a brand that correctly uses the five pillars we have seen before. They share product updates, share entertaining posts such as videos from customers or create music playlists for different seasons, and more.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c007fba elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"c007fba\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"331\" height=\"512\" src=\"https:\/\/creasquare.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/