ntent\/uploads\/2022\/11\/marketing-agency-instagram-account.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-17682\" alt=\"Marketing agency Instagram account\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https:\/\/creasquare.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/marketing-agency-instagram-account.png 512w, https:\/\/creasquare.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/marketing-agency-instagram-account-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/creasquare.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/marketing-agency-instagram-account-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/creasquare.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/marketing-agency-instagram-account-440x438.png 440w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2e228d3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2e228d3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This marketing brand is in charge of managing its clients&#8217; marketing activities, and its objective is to attract consumers, increase sales, strengthen branding, and generate market value.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d5dd902 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"d5dd902\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"333\" height=\"512\" src=\"https:\/\/creasquare.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/marketing-agency-instagram-posts.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-17683\" alt=\"Marketing agency Instagram posts\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https:\/\/creasquare.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/marketing-agency-instagram-posts.png 333w, https:\/\/creasquare.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/marketing-agency-instagram-posts-195x300.png 195w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 333px) 100vw, 333px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4a08503 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"4a08503\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As we can see in the photos, this brand is heavily relying on the engagement pillar, apart from giving information about the brand. They interact with their followers and invite them to participate in what they do.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Creating a relationship with your followers is something quite unique that will make you sustainably stand out. Like any other relationship, it guarantees feedback on the things you do. Whether the feedback highlights something good or bad about the brand is always helpful. It helps you to make changes in the way you are doing things, to understand your audience more, and to keep on growing.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8df7d5b elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"8df7d5b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Get Inspired!\n<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3bbb14d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3bbb14d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It is no news that some content pillars won\u2019t work for some companies but will for others. For example, content pillars related to life advice are probably better for companies that link to it and have an audience that will do that as well. In contrast, a real estate agent would probably lean on clients\u2019 opinions and testimonials as content pillars.\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Still, knowing more about content pillars can inspire you to make your own! Here we have a few examples of what content pillars could include.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Self-care and inspiring advice:<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-728149a elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"728149a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"306\" height=\"512\" src=\"https:\/\/creasquare.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/self-care-advice.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-17684\" alt=\"self care advice Instagram post\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https:\/\/creasquare.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/self-care-advice.jpeg 306w, https:\/\/creasquare.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/self-care-advice-179x300.jpeg 179w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 306px) 100vw, 306px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-dea4af7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"dea4af7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Product promotion:<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-722c2e3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"722c2e3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"329\" height=\"512\" src=\"https:\/\/creasquare.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/starbucks-product-promotion-instagram-post.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-17685\" alt=\"Starbucks product promotion Instagram post\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https:\/\/creasquare.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/starbucks-product-promotion-instagram-post.jpeg 329w, https:\/\/creasquare.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/starbucks-product-promotion-instagram-post-193x300.jpeg 193w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 329px) 100vw, 329px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a74a098 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a74a098\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Using humor to attract the audience:<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-20e864e elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"20e864e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;starto_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;starto_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"512\" height=\"358\" src=\"https:\/\/creasquare.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/shopify-tweet-using-humor.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-17686\" alt=\"Shopify tweet using humor\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https:\/\/creasquare.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/shopify-tweet-using-humor.jpeg 512w, https:\/\/creasquare.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/1